Father Joseph Witko: I saw Jesus in a white robe
He is a charismatic man.
Mass for the release and healing is attended by crowds.
He was ten years old when inexplicable things began to happen in his life.
Today, through the Franciscan, others are experiencing it.
Crowds attend Fr. Witko’s Mass for Liberation and Healing
Once the parents of a 7-month-old child who had a 7.5 mm hole in his heart came to him.
It was to be operated on.
Father Joseph Witko prayed over him.
On the same day, the boy was taken to the hospital for treatment.
Surprised doctors said: “The operation is not necessary, the loss is only 1.5 mm”.
The parents were crying with happiness.
After another prayer, the Franciscan hole disappeared completely.
The spiritual extraordinary actions of the Creator began to experience already as a teenager.
In his dreams, purgatory souls came to him asking for help.
I was awakened at night and urged to pray for the dead and those who died at that moment – he recalls.
He also experienced the presence of an evil spirit.
And he had a vision of what happens to a man who commits mortal sin.
“My body started to change.
I lost my human characteristics and began to look like an animal,” he says.
The invisible force lifted him up, he could not get his voice out.
He felt that he was lost.
Then God showed him salvation.
“Submerged in the waters of the river symbolising the holy baptism, I was released and returned to my human form...”, he says.
He did not tell anyone about these strange experiences.
His vocation matured in him.
He was 16 years old when he joined the Franciscans.
In his sermons he did not only want to talk about Jesus.
He wanted people to experience Him alive.
Members of the Charismatic Community of Renewal in the Holy Spirit
The healing masses celebrated by Father Witko are attended by many people who are counting on getting rid of the disease.
The priest emphasizes, however, that their main goal is spiritual healing, not bodily healing.
