Max Kolonko is cut off from KWW The Patriotic Revolution of Max Kolonko
KWW Patriotyczna Rewolucja Maxa Kolonko is the name of the electoral committee under which the political formation #R Revolution of Mariusz Maxa Kolonko was to go to the October parliamentary elections.
The revolution directed its proposal especially to young voters with right-wing views.
Prior to the elections, Kolonko announced cooperation with Marek Jakubiak or Paweł Kukisz, but neither of these coalitions occurred, and KWW Patriotyczna Rewolucja Maxa Kolonko himself did not even manage to collect enough signatures to put up lists in any constituency in Poland.
Now Kolonko has announced on Twitter that he has ended cooperation with KWW Patriotic Revolution Max Kolonko.
"I will wait for the above-mentioned KWW to delete my name from the name.
I kindly ask you not to associate my person with the above-mentioned entity”, he added and announced that more information will be provided soon.
